        "commands": [
          {
            "id": "8c6636f6-5cd1-474c-a6db-20a9d9ce64f5",
            "orderKey": 0,
            "state": "active",
            "commandId": "custom",
            "input": {
              "instructions": "Your job is to manage a prior authorization workflow end to end. You will retrieve a queue of patient authorization IDs, then for each one: download the authorization document, extract the relevant data, and use that data to fill out and submit a prior authorization form.\nFollow these steps exactly:\nStep 1 - Get the Auth ID queue Call the Browser Sort Order Agent :chip{\"id\":\"356bf695-3773-4933-bb06-b601b2ada78f\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}. It will return an array of Auth IDs.\nStep 2 - Process each Auth ID (loop) For every Auth ID in the array, run the following sequence in order:\n- 2a. Download and extract the document Pass the Auth ID to the Download File Agent :chip{\"id\":\"1736c253-fa95-4ca7-a2ce-30fb67fb631e\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}. It will download the patient's authorization document and internally delegate to the Read Agent :chip{\"id\":\"bcaa861a-7fb8-408a-bb0b-440e6c989de1\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}to extract all structured data needed for the form. It will return that extracted data to you.\n- 2b. Fill and submit the form Pass the extracted data to the Fill Form Agent :chip{\"id\":\"56868631-96cc-4d02-84eb-07fd9d883f93\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}. It will populate every required field in the prior authorization form and submit it.\nDo not proceed to the next Auth ID until the form for the current one has been successfully submitted."
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "b6875af8-023e-4520-b343-aaf32322565e",
            "orderKey": 1,
            "state": "active",
            "commandId": "callSpecializedAgent",
            "input": {
              "agent": ":chip{\"id\":\"356bf695-3773-4933-bb06-b601b2ada78f\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "34cce7ad-1ca0-484a-b267-6446d89bea46",
            "orderKey": 2,
            "state": "active",
            "commandId": "callSpecializedAgent",
            "input": {
              "agent": ":chip{\"id\":\"1736c253-fa95-4ca7-a2ce-30fb67fb631e\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}",
              "inputs": {
                "authID": "Auth ID of the user prior authirization being downloaded"
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "6f72c02a-de7d-4bf4-a1e7-ed09e05cd2c0",
            "orderKey": 3,
            "state": "active",
            "commandId": "callSpecializedAgent",
            "input": {
              "agent": ":chip{\"id\":\"56868631-96cc-4d02-84eb-07fd9d883f93\",\"groupId\":\"agent\"}",
              "inputs": {}
            }
          }
